                        <li class="p-0 m-0" style="padding-left: 0;"><a href="https://forum.effectivealtruism.org/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-eablue hover:text-cardinal"><iconify-icon icon="solar:chat-round-dots-linear"></iconify-icon> Effective Altruism Forum</a></li>
